  <script type="text/javascript">
  
 const loadBooks = () => {
      const xhttp = new XMLHttpRequest();

      xhttp.open("GET", "/nomination_hold", false);
      xhttp.send().then(
          const category_name = JSON.parse(xhttp.responseText);
      console.log(category_name);
       const x = `
           <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-12">
                <h1 style="text-align: center;">Nominations for ${category_name}</h1>
              </div>
              <hr class="center" style="width: 90%;">
            </div>

            <br/>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-1"></div>
              <div class="col-md-10">
                <h2>Nomination and Selection of ${category_name} Awardees</h2>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-1"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-1"></div>
              <div class="col-md-10">
                <p>Nomination to the Hwarang Heroes and Legends in ${category_name} Award is by invitation only. The names of the nominees and other information about the nominations cannot be revealed until 5 years later.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-1"></div>
            </div>

            <hr class="center" style="width: 90%;">

            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-1"></div>
              <div class="col-md-10">
                <h2>Process of Nomination and Selection</h2>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-1"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-1"></div>
              <div class="col-md-10">
                <p>NThe Hwarang Heroes and Legends Committee discusses the competent and qualified candidate during its monthly meetings.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-1"></div>
            </div>

            <hr class="center" style="width: 90%;">

            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-1"></div>
              <div class="col-md-10">
                <h2>Selection of Nobel Laureates</h2>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-1"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-1"></div>
              <div class="col-md-10">
                <p>The Hwarang Heroes and Legends Award Committee is responsible for the selection of the Heroes and Legends in ${category_name}. The Committee screens the nominations and presents a proposal for final candidates. The committee consists nominally of eleven voting members, but since many years, it also includes voting adjunct members. The Committee’s final proposal is discussed in a larger body, the Hwarang Youth Foundation, who has the final voting to nominate the candidate. It is in principle possible to suggest that no Prize be given the current month, but that is a seldom used choice.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-1"></div>
            </div>

            <hr class="center" style="width: 90%;">

            <div class="row">
